   <conbody>
      <div id="ThereAreTwoTypesOfBatteryTests.TheT-AEE9FFCA" class="- topic/div ">
         <p class="- topic/p ">There are
two types of battery tests. The tests can be started manually but
also be configured to automatically start at certain interval, if
allowed to start.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The battery circuit test checks that the battery
is available and ready to supply the load if the rectifier output
is reduced. </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">The battery capacity test will discharge the battery
either to a set capacity level or for a set duration.</p>
      </div>
